nnoremap <silent> <C-left> :wincmd h<CR>
nnoremap <silent> <C-Right> :wincmd l<CR>
map <leader>n :NERDTreeToggle<CR>
nnoremap <leader>nt <cmd>NERDTreeFind<cr>
map <C-z> :wq<CR>
nnoremap <leader>= <cmd>:%!bc -l<cr>
